GOMEZ LLC ATTORNEY AT LAW, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Diego VILLAQUIRAN and Gloria Villaquiran, Defendants-Petitioners. C-259 September Term 2018
081460 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 2, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004362-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
